item.title: Call of Duty: Black Ops - First Strike Multiplayer Preview [Official HD]
item.description:
Call of Duty: Black Ops - First Strike Multiplayer Preview [Official HD]
Available first on Xbox 360 February 1st. More details to come for PS3 and PC. First Strike contains 5 incredibly diverse maps spanning the globe; featuring 4 multiplayer maps and a new Zombie experience. Includes "Berlin Wall", allowing combat on both sides of the imposing wall; "Discovery", a desolate, frozen German outpost in the Arctic; "Kowloon", battle in the rain along the rooftops of a towering Chinese sprawl; "Stadium", an intense locale with a pro hockey arena backdrop; and "Ascension", where you fight zombies in a Soviet launch facility. Get all the latest news on www.callofduty.com and follow @JD_2020.
